These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, freelancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, western
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, reggae
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the coach##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | milk     | lemonade |
| Hobby         | woodworking  | singing       |
| Job           | freelancer   | coach    |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | rock     |
| Sport         | climbing | baseball      |
| Transport     | motorbike       | skateboard           |

