.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, kale
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, scientist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
4. the mexican is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | 7up         | iced-tea       |
| Food          | lettuce        | kale |
| Job           | scientist | entrepreneur    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts        | zombie  |
| Nationality   | mexican        | nigerian       |
| Pet           | rabbit            | turtle        |
| Transport     | roller            | helicopter       |

