2. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the engineer is on the left or right of the chef##3
5. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
