.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, baking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, animation
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, d&b
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, motorbike
1. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | 7up    | coffee   |
| Hobby         | baking | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | animation      | spy     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | techno        |
| Pet           | chinchilla        | hedgehog |
| Sport         | snowboarding    | lacrosse |
| Transport     | motorbike         | roller       |

