2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the mexican is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
6. the nurse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | mechanic    | nurse  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | horror    |
